            "text": " correspond to ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2Chronicles 26:21-23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " only.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(16) But when he was strong.—See 2Chronicles 26:15, “till he was strong,” and the same phrase, 2Chronicles 12:1.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(16) ",
            "children": []
