      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "for he transgressed against the Lord his God; who had helped him, and made him so great, and had bestowed so many favours upon him; the Targum is,\"the Word of the Lord his God;''what his transgression was, follows: ",
        "children": []
